## Educational Use License

This project is specifically developed for educational purposes, with a focus 
on rural schools in Odisha, India. 

### Special Provisions:
- ✅ **Free for Educational Institutions**: All educational institutions may use this software without charge
- ✅ **Rural School Priority**: Special support and priority access for rural and government schools
- ✅ **Cultural Preservation**: This software contributes to the preservation and promotion of Odia heritage
- ✅ **Community Benefit**: The platform serves the broader social good of improving rural education

### Smart India Hackathon 2024
This project was developed for the Smart India Hackathon 2024, focusing on 
improving rural education through culturally-integrated technology solutions.

### Attribution
When using this software, please provide appropriate attribution to the 
ShikshaMitra project and its mission to improve rural education in Odisha.
